# Per-person conscience state — stays local, never shared with a cofounder (DEC-001).
# Everything else BOSS writes (docs/ ideas, canvas, decisions, RESUME, and the venture
# brain's read.md) DOES commit — so pushing backs up your thinking AND keeps your
# cofounder in the loop. But the conscience's relationship with YOU — what it said and
# what you did with it — is yours alone; it never travels to a teammate.
